text: Diaaeldin Kamal Gouda Abdelmottaleb (born 2 May 1993) is a heavyweight freestyle wrestler from Egypt. In 2016 he won the African Championships and competed at the Rio Olympics, losing in the second bout to Komeil Ghasemi. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic wrestlers of Egypt Category:Wrestlers at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Egyptian male sport wrestlers
